<Layout
  title="High-Eng & Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI in Orange County"
  description="Luxury appliance repair in Orange County for Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Viking, Thermador, Gaggenau, La Cornue, AGA, and premium brands."
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <div style="margin: 50px">
    <section>
      <h2>Luxury Appliance Repair in Orange County, CA</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>White-glove appliance repair for high-end homes, coastal estates, and luxury kitchens across Orange County.</strong>
      </p>

      <p>
        Orange County homes often feature some of the most advanced and beautifully integrated appliances available — from built-in Sub-Zero refrigeration and Wolf ranges to Miele dishwashers, Thermador cooking appliances, Gaggenau ovens, Viking ranges, La Cornue ranges, AGA cookers, and other premium European and luxury brands.
      </p>

      <p>
        When one of these appliances stops working correctly, a standard repair approach is not enough. Luxury appliances require careful diagnostics, brand-specific experience, proper parts, and a technician who understands how to work inside high-value homes with cleanliness, discretion, and respect.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI</strong> provides high-end appliance repair in Orange County for homeowners, property managers, designers, and estate managers who expect professional service from the first call to the final walkthrough.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Why Orange County Homeowners Choose ZARICCI</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Luxury and European Brand Experience</strong><br />
          We focus on premium appliance brands such as Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, Viking, Gaggenau, La Cornue, AGA, Bertazzoni, Bosch, Cove, JennAir, Monogram, Dacor, Fisher & Paykel, and True Residential.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Service for Built-In and Integrated Appliances</strong><br />
          Many Orange County homes have panel-ready refrigerators, built-in wine preservation systems, concealed dishwashers, professional ranges, and custom kitchen layouts. Our technicians understand how to diagnose and service these appliances carefully.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Same-Day and Priority Scheduling When Available</strong><br />
          We offer convenient scheduling for Orange County customers, including urgent appliance repair needs when appointments are available.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clean, Discreet, White-Glove Service</strong><br />
          We treat your home with care, protect surrounding surfaces, communicate clearly, and maintain a professional repair experience from start to finish.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear Estimates Before Repair Work Begins</strong><br />
          After diagnosing the appliance, we explain the issue, repair options, estimated cost, and parts needs before moving forward.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>High-End Appliances We Repair in Orange County</h3>

      <h4>Luxury Refrigerator and Freezer Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We repair built-in refrigerators, column refrigerators, freezer drawers, undercounter refrigeration, and integrated cooling systems from brands like Sub-Zero, Thermador, Miele, Viking, Monogram, True Residential, Fisher & Paykel, and Gaggenau.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Refrigerator not cooling properly</li>
        <li>Freezer temperature problems</li>
        <li>Ice maker failure</li>
        <li>Water dispenser problems</li>
        <li>Excess frost or moisture buildup</li>
        <li>Compressor, fan, sensor, and control board issues</li>
        <li>Door seal, hinge, and custom panel alignment problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Luxury Range, Oven, Stove, and Cooktop Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We service professional cooking appliances including Wolf ranges, Viking ranges, Thermador ovens, Gaggenau wall ovens, La Cornue ranges, AGA cookers, Bertazzoni ranges, ILVE ranges, Fulgor Milano cooking appliances, BlueStar ranges, and other premium brands.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Burners not igniting</li>
        <li>Oven not heating</li>
        <li>Uneven baking or roasting</li>
        <li>Gas smell or ignition clicking</li>
        <li>Induction cooktop errors</li>
        <li>Control panel, relay board, thermostat, and sensor failures</li>
        <li>Door, hinge, gasket, and temperature calibration issues</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Premium Dishwasher Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We repair high-end dishwashers from Miele, Bosch, Cove, Thermador, Fisher & Paykel, Viking, JennAir, and other premium brands commonly installed in luxury Orange County kitchens.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Dishwasher not draining</li>
        <li>Poor cleaning performance</li>
        <li>Water leaks</li>
        <li>Cycle interruption</li>
        <li>Error codes</li>
        <li>Panel-ready dishwasher door issues</li>
        <li>Pump, heater, sensor, and control board problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Luxury Washer and Dryer Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We service premium laundry appliances from Miele, Bosch, LG Signature, Electrolux, Fisher & Paykel, and other high-performance laundry brands.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Washer not draining or spinning</li>
        <li>Dryer not heating</li>
        <li>Long drying times</li>
        <li>Vibration or noise issues</li>
        <li>Water leaks</li>
        <li>Control panel and sensor problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Wine Cooler, Beverage Center, and Specialty Appliance Repair</h4>

      <p>
        Orange County homes often include specialty appliances such as wine coolers, beverage centers, built-in coffee machines, warming drawers, steam ovens, speed ovens, ice makers, and outdoor kitchen appliances.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Wine cooler not holding temperature</li>
        <li>Beverage center cooling issues</li>
        <li>Built-in coffee machine problems</li>
        <li>Steam oven or speed oven errors</li>
        <li>Warming drawer not heating</li>
        <li>Ice maker failures</li>
        <li>Outdoor BBQ grill and outdoor kitchen appliance issues</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

