      <h3>Our Orange County Luxury Appliance Repair Process</h3>

      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Schedule Your Appointment</strong><br />
          Call or book online and tell us the appliance brand, appliance type, model if available, and the issue you are experiencing.
