    <section>
      <h3>Luxury Appliance Repair for Coastal Homes, Estates, and Custom Kitchens</h3>

      <p>
        Orange County kitchens are often designed around premium appliances, custom cabinetry, built-in refrigeration, imported ranges, and integrated smart-home features. A careless repair can damage panels, flooring, finishes, or the appliance itself.
      </p>

      <p>
        At <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI</strong>, our service is designed for homes where quality matters. We focus on accurate diagnosis, careful handling, clear communication, and a repair experience that matches the standards of a luxury home.
